00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:13,700
You have achieved some success in the Mist and Clouds Sword Dance.

26
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:18,390
I remember practicing the Sleeve Swordplay when I was young too.

27
00:02:18,390 --> 00:02:23,970
Watching you today reminds me of my younger self.

28
00:02:23,970 --> 00:02:30,470
Master, you're still quite young now and as otherworldly as ever.

29
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:35,610
People as graceful as us must learn the most beautiful martial arts.

30
00:02:35,610 --> 00:02:42,040
Then we must be stunningly magnificent every time we make an appearance.

31
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:44,480
Like you?

32
00:02:44,970 --> 00:02:48,980
With handsome men carrying the palanquin, maidservants leading the way,

33
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:53,570
and a light veil hanging down covering half of your face?

34
00:02:54,220 --> 00:02:57,980
That's now. When I was younger...

35
00:02:57,980 --> 00:03:00,610
I was financially strained.

36
00:03:00,610 --> 00:03:04,770
I couldn't afford palanquins or maidservants.

37
00:03:04,770 --> 00:03:08,640
Then how did you make an appearance back then?

38
00:03:09,490 --> 00:03:11,830
Watch carefully.

39
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:19,220
When people as graceful as us make an appearance,

40
00:03:19,220 --> 00:03:22,770
first of all, there must be a sound and an aesthetic mood.

41
00:03:22,770 --> 00:03:26,490
With your hands behind your back, land yourself elegantly,

42
00:03:26,490 --> 00:03:31,570
revealing your transcendent back before turning your head slightly.

43
00:03:32,490 --> 00:03:35,210
- For a self-introduction? 
 - No.

44
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:38,700
This is just what comes first.

45
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:44,660
Wait until everyone exclaims, then in a leisurely tone you say,

46
00:03:44,660 --> 00:03:53,490
"I apologize for being late. If you want to do anything here, you'll need to defeat me first."

47
00:03:53,490 --> 00:03:59,020
However Master, what do I do if they're not impressed?

48
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:06,960
Just wait.

49
00:04:07,670 --> 00:04:10,340
There will definitely be those who are amazed.

50
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:15,730
Then, just don't say anything else.

51
00:04:15,730 --> 00:04:22,200
Show a few moves and defeat your opponent before you turn around,

52
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:27,130
stand sideways, and say,

53
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:30,460
"I am..."

54
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:32,030
"I am..."

55
00:04:32,030 --> 00:04:34,250
"Young Master Liu Yue."

56
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:38,370
"Fairy... Luoxia?"

57
00:04:38,370 --> 00:04:42,170
That's right, exactly. You practice it now.

58
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:44,000
In front of you?

59
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,940
Of course. Is that a problem?

60
00:04:46,940 --> 00:04:50,230
It's really... embarrassing.

61
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:52,000
What's there to be embarrassed about?

62
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:56,340
You can ask for advice from your martial uncle, Luo Xuan.

63
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:58,320
This is called "style."

64
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:01,280
It's not being pretentious. Don't feel pressured.

65
00:05:02,780 --> 00:05:04,830
Yes, Master!

66
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:09,560
All right. I'm leaving. You keep practicing.

67
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:33,360
I am Fairy Luoxia.

68
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:37,790
I am Fairy Luoxia.

69
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:43,180
I am... Fairy Luoxia.

70
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:50,130
This is too embarrassing. Why am I actually practicing?

71
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:07,320
Right.

72
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:11,390
Why am I...

73
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:16,100
actually practicing?

74
00:06:18,375 --> 00:06:22,125

75
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,790
Miss.

76
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:48,370
You've become a disciple of the Academy. What now?

77
00:06:48,370 --> 00:06:51,090
Do you still remember Tian Wai Tian?

78
00:06:51,090 --> 00:06:57,030
I didn't act according to the plan that day, so your anger towards me makes sense.

79
00:07:01,170 --> 00:07:04,730
Miss, not at all. I dare not.

80
00:07:04,730 --> 00:07:09,107
I was going to look for you after walking Baili Dongjun to Qinglong Gate that day,

81
00:07:09,107 --> 00:07:12,340
but I didn't expect that Master Liu Yue would take me in.

82
00:07:12,340 --> 00:07:16,760
I came to see you today as soon as I found an opportunity.

83
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:24,960
But why didn't you take Baili Dongjun to the path Yuji was on that day?

84
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:27,470
After several assassination attempts that day,

85
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:29,960
Baili Dongjun's nerves had reached a state of extreme tension.

86
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:35,390
If he went down that path and met Yuji, was defeated, and then taken by us,

87
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:39,640
with his temperament, Xunian Technique aside,

88
00:07:40,470 --> 00:07:43,320
I was afraid he'd find an opportunity to go down with us.

89
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,790
This was the first reason.

90
00:07:44,790 --> 00:07:46,690
Secondly,

91
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:49,610
I was wondering...

92
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:55,050
if this was the only way to restore our nation.

93
00:07:55,050 --> 00:07:57,030
What do you mean?

94
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,910
It's not that

95
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:03,250
I have a better plan yet.

96
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:06,080
We'll talk about it later.

97
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,390
Qixuan, I have to go now.

98
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:11,130
I'll continue to observe Baili Dongjun.

99
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:16,270
Once I decide what to do, I'll contact you.

100
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:20,570
As for Yuji, please help me explain this to him.

101
00:08:26,470 --> 00:08:28,130
Miss.

102
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,980
Is there anything else?

103
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:37,690
 Should I tell you that there's another natural martial artist?

104
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,070
Nothing.

105
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:49,180
Please take good care of yourself, Young Miss.

106
00:08:55,940 --> 00:09:01,420
 Is this the only way to restore our nation?

107
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:03,450
Miss.

108
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:09,440
What exactly are you planning to do?

109
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,450
Disciple.

110
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,900
Master?

111
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:54,230
That's enough.

112
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:57,900
It seems today is not a good day for playing GO.

113
00:09:57,900 --> 00:10:00,030
You should go rest early.

114
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,980
Master...

115
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:12,210
Do you think I'd ask you where you were?

116
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:18,020
What does that have to do with me?

117
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:23,180
I was just bored and wanted to play GO with you.

118
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:31,140
Master...

119
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:33,540
Now can you focus on playing GO?

120
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:40,100
Come on. Let's play.

121
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:50,460
That's more like it.

122
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:13,280
 Brother Yun, this is for you!

123
00:11:16,380 --> 00:11:17,700
 What's this?

124
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:20,280
 My mother started teaching me needlework.

125
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:23,720
 This is the first pouch I embroidered.

126
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:30,620
 Wenjun, this is so beautiful. I like it very much.

127
00:11:41,900 --> 00:11:51,300
 Even if I could have predicted everything, I couldn't have foreseen our reunion to be like this.

128
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:55,060
 Can you tell me about the world outside?

129
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:58,440
 Once you're done, I'll let you go.

130
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:06,880
 I have been staying here for a long time.

131
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:16,280
 Like this dish, Caged Bird,

132
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:24,940
 I am caged. But I long for... the world outside.

133
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:41,940
 I wonder if I suggested taking her out of here, would she be willing.

134
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:25,260
You're back.

135
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:31,760
I met Young Miss today.

136
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:37,040
What was her explanation?

137
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:41,100
I'll explain the details to you later.

138
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:42,980
However, there's one thing that we can confirm.

139
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:46,680
She hasn't betrayed Tian Wai Tian.

140
00:14:48,180 --> 00:14:49,420
That's good.

141
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:53,640
Are there any other instructions from Lord Wuxiang?

142
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:57,340
He instructed us to give a great gift...

143
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:02,120
to the imperial family of Beili.

144
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:09,540
What? You're saying that Ye Dingzhi is Ye Yun?

145
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:12,340
You mean the son of Ye Yu?

146
00:15:15,020 --> 00:15:17,580
No wonder he didn't want the imperial jade seal.

147
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:21,860
No wonder he said I could definitely provide him with what he wants.

148
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:26,200
What he wants... is my life.

149
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:31,500
Saddle the horses. Now!

150
00:15:31,500 --> 00:15:34,380
I'm going to the palace.

151
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:14,100
Good morning, Ye Dingzhi.

152
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:18,260
Good morning, Miss.

153
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:28,540
You weren't done with the previous story.

154
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:31,100
We'll talk about the Buddhist States today.

155
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:32,700
Sure.

156
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:36,000
Give me a minute. I'll go wash my face.

